Package com.ibm.team.scm.client.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IChangeHistoryEvent
    Generic event type to describe the flow of change from or to a particular workspace connection.
    ICommitEvent
    Event type for committing a new state to a change set in a workspace.
    IComponentHierarchyUpdateEvent
    Generic event type which describes updates which have happened to a workspace's component hierarchy.
    IConfigurationUpdateEvent
    Generic event type which describes updates which have happened to a workspace's configuration.
    ICurrentChangeSetEvent
    Event type which describes when the current active change set for a workspace connection's component changes.
    ILockEvent
    Generic event type to describe the stream and component lock changes on a workspace connection.
    IPatchUpdateEvent
    Event that is fired from a workspace connection when the accept queue or current patch changes for one or more components in the workspace.
    IWorkItemsModificationEvent Deprecated
    This event has not been fired in quite some time.
    IWorkspaceEvent
    Generic event type which describes updates which have happened to a workspace connection.
